{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1354,"text":"Virtual reality started for me\nin sort of an unusual place."},{"time":6976,"text":"It was the 1970s."},{"time":9173,"text":"I got into the field very young:\nI was seven years old."},{"time":12383,"text":"And the tool that I used \nto access virtual reality"},{"time":17245,"text":"was the Evel Knievel stunt cycle."},{"time":20810,"text":"This is a commercial for \nthat particular item:"},{"time":23201,"text":"(Video) Voice-over: What a jump!"},{"time":24776,"text":"Evel's riding the amazing stunt cycle."},{"time":26767,"text":"That gyro-power sends him \nover 100 feet at top speed."}]},{"cues":[{"time":29536,"text":"Chris Milk: So this was my joy back then."},{"time":31628,"text":"I rode this motorcycle everywhere."},{"time":34587,"text":"And I was there with Evel Knievel; we \njumped the Snake River Canyon together."},{"time":38847,"text":"I wanted the rocket."},{"time":40216,"text":"I never got the rocket,\nI only got the motorcycle."},{"time":45626,"text":"I felt so connected to this world."},{"time":48203,"text":"I didn't want to be a storyteller \nwhen I grew up, I wanted to be stuntman."},{"time":52440,"text":"I was there. Evel Knievel was my friend."},{"time":55644,"text":"I had so much empathy for him."}]},{"cues":[{"time":58747,"text":"But it didn't work out. (Laughter)"},{"time":61358,"text":"I went to art school."},{"time":63382,"text":"I started making music videos."},{"time":65792,"text":"And this is one of the early\nmusic videos that I made:"},{"time":68866,"text":"(Music: \"Touch the Sky\" by Kanye West)"},{"time":74756,"text":"CM: You may notice \nsome slight similarities here."},{"time":78032,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":79818,"text":"And I got that rocket."},{"time":82461,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":85104,"text":"So, now I'm a filmmaker,\nor, the beginning of a filmmaker,"},{"time":89509,"text":"and I started using the tools that are\navailable to me as a filmmaker"},{"time":93243,"text":"to try to tell the most compelling stories\nthat I can to an audience."},{"time":97831,"text":"And film is this incredible medium\nthat allows us to feel empathy"},{"time":100980,"text":"for people that are very different than us"},{"time":103006,"text":"and worlds completely \nforeign from our own."}]},{"cues":[{"time":105838,"text":"Unfortunately,"},{"time":106668,"text":"Evel Knievel did not feel the same \nempathy for us that we felt for him,"},{"time":111527,"text":"and he sued us for this video --"},{"time":114330,"text":"(Laughter) --"},{"time":116061,"text":"shortly thereafter."},{"time":118110,"text":"On the upside, the man \nthat I worshipped as a child,"},{"time":122950,"text":"the man that I wanted \nto become as an adult,"},{"time":126066,"text":"I was finally able to get his autograph."},{"time":130556,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":137832,"text":"Let's talk about film now."},{"time":142849,"text":"Film, it's an incredible medium,"},{"time":145745,"text":"but essentially, it's the same\nnow as it was then."},{"time":149060,"text":"It's a group of rectangles that are\nplayed in a sequence."},{"time":152529,"text":"And we've done incredible things\nwith those rectangles."},{"time":156362,"text":"But I started thinking about,"},{"time":159247,"text":"is there a way that I can use modern\nand developing technologies"},{"time":163616,"text":"to tell stories in different ways"},{"time":165741,"text":"and tell different kinds of stories"},{"time":167482,"text":"that maybe I couldn't tell using\nthe traditional tools of filmmaking"},{"time":171793,"text":"that we've been using for 100 years?"},{"time":173964,"text":"So I started experimenting,"},{"time":176785,"text":"and what I was trying to do was\nto build the ultimate empathy machine."},{"time":183054,"text":"And here's one of the early experiments:"},{"time":185588,"text":"(Music)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":188412,"text":"So this is called\n\"The Wilderness Downtown.\""},{"time":190656,"text":"It was a collaboration with Arcade Fire."},{"time":192712,"text":"It asked you to put in the address\nwhere you grew up at the beginning of it."},{"time":196362,"text":"It's a website."},{"time":197359,"text":"And out of it starts growing these little\nboxes with different browser windows."},{"time":202275,"text":"And you see this teenager \nrunning down a street,"},{"time":204657,"text":"and then you see Google Street View\nand Google Maps imagery"},{"time":207415,"text":"and you realize the street\nhe's running down is yours."},{"time":209939,"text":"And when he stops in front of a house,\nhe stops in front of your house."},{"time":215735,"text":"And this was great, and I saw people \nhaving an even deeper emotional reaction"},{"time":219417,"text":"to this than the things that \nI had made in rectangles."},{"time":222631,"text":"And I'm essentially taking \na piece of your history"},{"time":226562,"text":"and putting it inside \nthe framing of the story."}]},{"cues":[{"time":229981,"text":"But then I started thinking,"},{"time":231578,"text":"okay, well that's a part of you,"},{"time":233430,"text":"but how do I put all of you\ninside of the frame?"},{"time":238731,"text":"So to do that, I started\nmaking art installations."},{"time":241834,"text":"And this is one called \n\"The Treachery of Sanctuary.\""},{"time":244374,"text":"It's a triptych. I'm going to show\nyou the third panel."},{"time":247392,"text":"(Music)"},{"time":271260,"text":"So now I've got you inside of the frame,"},{"time":274848,"text":"and I saw people having even more\nvisceral emotional reactions"},{"time":279403,"text":"to this work than the previous one."}]},{"cues":[{"time":282080,"text":"But then I started thinking about frames,\nand what do they represent?"},{"time":286230,"text":"And a frame is just a window."},{"time":288487,"text":"I mean, all the media that we watch --\ntelevision, cinema --"},{"time":291566,"text":"they're these windows into \nthese other worlds."},{"time":293819,"text":"And I thought, well, great. \nI got you in a frame."},{"time":296507,"text":"But I don't want you in the frame,\nI don't want you in the window,"},{"time":299634,"text":"I want you through the window,\nI want you on the other side,"},{"time":302523,"text":"in the world, inhabiting the world."}]},{"cues":[{"time":306218,"text":"So that leads me back to virtual reality."},{"time":309123,"text":"Let's talk about virtual reality."},{"time":312634,"text":"Unfortunately,\n"},{"time":313934,"text":"talking about virtual reality\nis like dancing about architecture."},{"time":318423,"text":"And this is actually someone dancing\nabout architecture in virtual reality."},{"time":325340,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":327823,"text":"So, it's difficult to explain.\nWhy is it difficult to explain?"},{"time":331084,"text":"It's difficult because it's a very \nexperiential medium."},{"time":334782,"text":"You feel your way inside of it."},{"time":336698,"text":"It's a machine, but inside of it,"},{"time":338496,"text":"it feels like real life,\nit feels like truth."},{"time":341945,"text":"And you feel present in the world\nthat you're inside"},{"time":344466,"text":"and you feel present with the people\nthat you're inside of it with.\n"}]},{"cues":[{"time":347689,"text":"So, I'm going to show you a demo\nof a virtual reality film:"},{"time":351785,"text":"a full-screen version of\nall the information"},{"time":354006,"text":"that we capture when\nwe shoot virtual reality."},{"time":356209,"text":"So we're shooting in every direction."},{"time":358034,"text":"This is a camera system that we built"},{"time":360210,"text":"that has 3D cameras that look\nin every direction"},{"time":363235,"text":"and binaural microphones\nthat face in every direction."},{"time":365987,"text":"We take this and we build, basically,\na sphere of a world that you inhabit."},{"time":371333,"text":"So what I'm going to show you\nis not a view into the world,"},{"time":374736,"text":"it's basically the whole world\nstretched into a rectangle."},{"time":378107,"text":"So this film is called \n\"Clouds Over Sidra,\""},{"time":381495,"text":"and it was made in conjunction with \nour virtual reality company called VRSE"},{"time":385989,"text":"and the United Nations,"},{"time":387755,"text":"and a co-collaborator named Gabo Arora."},{"time":390788,"text":"And we went to a Syrian refugee camp\nin Jordan in December"},{"time":394625,"text":"and shot the story of a 12-year-old\ngirl there named Sidra."},{"time":398982,"text":"And she and her family fled Syria\nthrough the desert into Jordan"},{"time":402473,"text":"and she's been living in this\ncamp for the last year and a half."}]},{"cues":[{"time":408207,"text":"(Video) Sidra: My name is Sidra."},{"time":410720,"text":"I am 12 years old."},{"time":412616,"text":"I am in the fifth grade."},{"time":414418,"text":"I am from Syria,\nin the Daraa Province, Inkhil City."},{"time":419605,"text":"I have lived here in the Zaatari camp\nin Jordan for the last year and a half."},{"time":426923,"text":"I have a big family:\n"},{"time":428931,"text":"three brothers, one is a baby."},{"time":431697,"text":"He cries a lot."},{"time":435142,"text":"I asked my father if I cried when \nI was a baby and he says I did not."},{"time":440197,"text":"I think I was a stronger baby\nthan my brother."}]},{"cues":[{"time":443821,"text":"CM: So, when you're inside \nof the headset."},{"time":446731,"text":"you're not seeing it like this."},{"time":448351,"text":"You're looking around through this world."},{"time":450423,"text":"You'll notice you see full\n360 degrees, in all directions."},{"time":455711,"text":"And when you're sitting there\nin her room, watching her,"},{"time":458702,"text":"you're not watching it through\na television screen,"},{"time":461115,"text":"you're not watching it through a window,\nyou're sitting there with her."},{"time":464523,"text":"When you look down, you're sitting\non the same ground that she's sitting on."},{"time":468915,"text":"And because of that,"},{"time":470666,"text":"you feel her humanity in a deeper way."},{"time":475054,"text":"You empathize with her in a deeper way."}]},{"cues":[{"time":479590,"text":"And I think that we can change\nminds with this machine."},{"time":485917,"text":"And we've already started\nto try to change a few."},{"time":489690,"text":"So we took this film to the World Economic\nForum in Davos in January."},{"time":494536,"text":"And we showed it to a group of people"},{"time":497022,"text":"whose decisions affect the lives\nof millions of people."},{"time":501102,"text":"And these are people \nwho might not otherwise"},{"time":503220,"text":"be sitting in a tent \nin a refugee camp in Jordan."},{"time":509484,"text":"But in January, one afternoon\nin Switzerland,"},{"time":515813,"text":"they suddenly all found themselves there."},{"time":520309,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":526699,"text":"And they were affected by it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":529058,"text":"So we're going to make more of them."},{"time":532374,"text":"We're working with the \nUnited Nations right now"},{"time":535460,"text":"to shoot a whole series of these films."},{"time":537515,"text":"We just finished shooting\na story in Liberia."},{"time":540187,"text":"And now, we're going \nto shoot a story in India."},{"time":543633,"text":"And we're taking these films,"},{"time":545511,"text":"and we're showing them \nat the United Nations"},{"time":548036,"text":"to people that work there and people\nthat are visiting there."},{"time":551023,"text":"And we're showing \nthem to the people"},{"time":552810,"text":"that can actually change the lives\nof the people inside of the films."}]},{"cues":[{"time":557274,"text":"And that's where I think we just\nstart to scratch the surface"},{"time":560955,"text":"of the true power of virtual reality."},{"time":564614,"text":"It's not a video game peripheral."},{"time":566835,"text":"It connects humans to other humans\nin a profound way"},{"time":571408,"text":"that I've never seen before \nin any other form of media."},{"time":574873,"text":"And it can change people's\nperception of each other."},{"time":578612,"text":"And that's how I think"},{"time":580298,"text":"virtual reality has the potential\nto actually change the world."}]},{"cues":[{"time":586604,"text":"So, it's a machine,"},{"time":589151,"text":"but through this machine\nwe become more compassionate,"},{"time":594074,"text":"we become more empathetic,\nand we become more connected."},{"time":599667,"text":"And ultimately, we become more human."}]},{"cues":[{"time":604491,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":605651,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}